## üõ†Ô∏è **Troubleshooting**

**"Wayland Detected" warning at startup?**
‚Üí See [Wayland Compatibility](#wayland-compatibility) section above. Run EVE without `PROTON_ENABLE_WAYLAND` or use an X11 session.

**No windows detected / empty window list?**
‚Üí Check if running pure Wayland: `echo $XDG_SESSION_TYPE`. If "wayland" and `echo $DISPLAY` is empty, X11 tools won't work.

**Characters not found for settings sync?**
‚Üí Add custom EVE installation path in Settings Sync tab

**Windows not auto-arranging?**
‚Üí Ensure character names match EVE window titles

**High CPU usage?**
‚Üí Reduce refresh rate or number of active previews

